.TH ZOPEN-USAGE "1" "June 2026" "zopen tools 0.8.5" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
zopen-usage \- manual page for zopen-usage 0.8.5
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B zopen-usage
[\fI\,OPTION\/\fR] [\fI\,ZOPEN_ROOTFS\/\fR] [\fI\,PARAMETERS\/\fR]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
zopen\-usage is a utility to display the file system usage by a zopen environment
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-pie\fR
generate a pie chart showing space hogs
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR, \-?
display this help and exit.
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
run in verbose mode.
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
print version
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
zopen usage
list the file system usage for the environment
.TP
zopen usage \-\-pie /mnt/zopen
list the file system usage for the zopen environment
at the mount point /mnt/zopen
.SS "Notes:"
.IP
Values might not add to 100% due to rounding during calculations; use the
reported values as guidance, rounding up for capacity planning for example.
